      "role": "user",
      "content": "it is just... constant. even when i'm alone i feel like i'm performing. and i know that if i actually lived my life the way i want to, people would just hate me or make it impossible. it feels like there's no way to win. everything is just so exhausting and i dont see a version of the future where it gets easier. it just feels like a losing game.",
