      "content": "but even stopping the fight feels like it's not enough. like even if i just try to rest, the whole world is still there, waiting to push back again. it just feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and stop the fighting is to just... not be part of it anymore. i mean, if the game is fundamentally rigged against me, why does it even make sense to keep playing?",
